  ('promotion-7fec267e-moex-00129', 'promotion-7fec267e', 'promotion-7fec267e-moex-110-b96fcbef', 'sub-promotion-7fec267e-02', NULL, 'essay', '甲男與乙女為上下樓層之鄰居，常有嫌隙。乙常在自家陽台澆花。一日
