  ('promotion-7fec267e-moex-00130', 'promotion-7fec267e', 'promotion-7fec267e-moex-110-b96fcbef', 'sub-promotion-7fec267e-02', NULL, 'essay', '某甲之子某乙為國一生，透過購物網站購買韓團的偶像公仔與周邊商
